# csshX

> Cluster SSH tool for macOS
> More information: https://github.com/brockgr/csshx

- Connect to multiple hosts:

`csshX {string some description 1: hostname} {string some description 2: hostname}`

- Connect to multiple hosts with a specific SSH key:

`csshX {string some description 1: user@hostname} {string some description 2: user@hostname} --ssh_args "-i {file key file with mandatory .pem extension}"`

- Connect to a pre-defined cluster from `/etc/clusters`:

`csshX cluster1`
